tps://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31929374&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=20918783256827453702b276_60150693"/><published>2025-05-16T20:22:11+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>069b98897735d9813b52f043841e3d89</id><title>我是誰？之（窮人翻身術)</title><updated>2025-05-16T20:37:53+08:00</updated><author><name>獨步走</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-16T20:37:53+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572434706"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572434706"&gt;香港有很多山頭墳墓&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;那些風水好的墳墓—般都是用水泥封住，霸佔土地及隔阻有人挖墓，破壞風水及偷取墓里財物&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;窮人改運，在自己祖先骨粉或頭髮或骨頭上滴1滴手指尖的鮮血，將小許偷放在墓中棺材蓋上，或打破墓上水泥，在水泥下見墳土的裂縫中放小許&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;7天後必將墓中之氣改轉到自己身上&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;警告，此乃偷天改遠之法，本人不建議用之。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;如有人用之，一切因果自負，與本人旡關。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31929383&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=20918783256827453702b276_60150693"/><published>2025-05-16T20:37:53+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2c3ab3bd5406d26df4dd972417ce8b5c</id><title>飲食業玩完</title><updated>2025-05-16T20:55:39+08:00</updated><author><name>精神裁判</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-16T20:55:39+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572434888"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572434888"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16229502" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572434888" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250516/20250516_e886e90abce8d3a